Who is Vedal? For the blind, He is the vision. For the hungry, He is the chef. For the thirsty, He is the water. If Vedal thinks, I agree. If Vedal speaks, I’m listening. If Vedal has one fan, it is me. If Vedal has no fans, I don’t exist.
